# === Monorepo Nexo — gitignore raíz ===

# Dependencias
**/node_modules

# Builds
**/dist
**/build

# Entorno — solo los .example se commitean
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example

# Archivos subidos / generados
api/uploads/*
!api/uploads/.gitkeep
api/invoices/*
!api/invoices/.gitkeep

# Tests
**/coverage

# Sistema / editores
.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea
*.log
